    "plan_content": "Here's the complete plan — only **`src/pipelines.js`** needs to change, with exactly **4 targeted edits**:\n\n---\n\n### Change 1 — Import `AutoModelForImageTextToText` (~line 43)\nAdd it to the existing `import { ... } from './models.js'` block, after `AutoModelForImageFeatureExtraction`.\n\n---\n\n### Change 2 — New `ImageTextToTextPipeline` class (after line 2779)\nInsert after `DocumentQuestionAnsweringPipeline` closes. The class:\n- Uses the standard `typedef → @callback → @typedef PipelineType → JSDoc → export class` pattern\n- `_call(image, text, generate_kwargs = {})`:\n  1. `prepareImages(image)[0]` → `processor(...)` → `pixel_values`\n  2. `tokenizer(text, { padding, truncation })` → `input_ids`\n  3. `model.generate({ inputs: pixel_values, input_ids, ...generate_kwargs })`\n  4. `tokenizer.batch_decode(output, { skip_special_tokens: true })` → `[{ generated_text }]`\n- Batch size 1 only (matches `DocumentQuestionAnsweringPipeline`)\n\n---\n\n### Change 3 — `SUPPORTED_TASKS` entry (after line 3341)\n```js\n\"image-text-to-text\": {\n    \"tokenizer\": AutoTokenizer,\n    \"pipeline\": ImageTextToTextPipeline,\n    \"model\": AutoModelForImageTextToText,\n    \"processor\": AutoProcessor,\n    \"default\": { \"model\": \"onnx-community/Florence-2-base-ft\" },\n    \"type\": \"multimodal\",\n},\n```\nInserted between `\"document-question-answering\"` and `\"image-to-image\"`.\n\n---\n\n### Change 4 — Factory JSDoc bullet (~line 3428)\nAdd `` - `\"image-text-to-text\"`: will return a `ImageTextToTextPipeline`. `` after the `\"image-to-text\"` bullet.\n\n---\n\n**No changes** to `src/models.js` — `AutoModelForImageTextToText` is already exported from there.",
